the stranger ( simplified chinese : &lt;unk&gt; ; traditional chinese : &lt;unk&gt; ; pinyin : &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 2014 hong kong drama film written and directed by michael apted . the film premiered at the 2014 sundance film festival on january 17 , 2014 . the film was selected as the dutch entry for the best foreign language film at the 87th academy awards , but was not nominated .